{"id":159,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":159,"title":"2 Corinthians 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Second Epistle of",["br"],"Paul the Apostle to the",["br"],["span.dominant","Corinthians"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","God comforts and cares for His Saints—The Saints are sealed and given assurance by the Spirit in their hearts."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.1","order":"03.10.001.18408"},["b","1"],"Paul, an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"apostle"],"of Jesus Christ by the will of God, and Timothy",["i","our"],"brother, unto the church of God which is at Corinth, with all the saints which are in all Achaia:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.2","order":"03.10.001.18409"},["b","2"],"Grace",["i","be"],"to you and peace from God our Father, and",["i","from"],"the Lord Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.3","order":"03.10.001.18410"},["b","3"],"Blessed",["i","be"],"God, even the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, the Father of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"mercies"],", and the God of all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"comfort"],";"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.4","order":"03.10.001.18411"},["b","4"],"Who comforteth us in all our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"tribulation"],", that we may be able to comfort them which are in any trouble, by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"comfort"],"wherewith we ourselves are comforted of God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.5","order":"03.10.001.18412"},["b","5"],"For as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"sufferings"],"of Christ abound in us, so our consolation also aboundeth by Christ."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.6","order":"03.10.001.18413"},["b","6"],"And whether we be afflicted,",["i","it is"],"for your consolation and salvation, which is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"effectual"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"enduring"],"of the same sufferings which we also suffer: or whether we be comforted,",["i","it is"],"for your consolation and salvation."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.7","order":"03.10.001.18414"},["b","7"],"And our hope of you",["i","is"],"steadfast, knowing, that as ye are partakers of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"sufferings"],", so",["i","shall ye be"],"also of the consolation."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.8","order":"03.10.001.18415"},["b","8"],"For we would not, brethren, have you ignorant of our trouble which came to us in Asia, that we were pressed out of measure, above strength, insomuch that we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"despaired"],"even of life:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.9","order":"03.10.001.18416"},["b","9"],"But we had the sentence of death in ourselves, that we should not trust in ourselves, but in God which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"raiseth"],"the dead:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.10","order":"03.10.001.18417"},["b","10"],"Who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"delivered"],"us from so great a death, and doth deliver: in whom we trust that he will yet deliver",["i","us;"]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.11","order":"03.10.001.18418"},["b","11"],"Ye also helping together by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"prayer"],"for us, that for the gift",["i","bestowed"],"upon us by the means of many persons thanks may be given by many on our behalf."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.12","order":"03.10.001.18419"},["b","12"],"For our rejoicing is this, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"testimony"],"of our conscience, that in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"simplicity"],"and godly sincerity, not with fleshly",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"wisdom"],", but by the grace of God, we have had our conversation in the world, and more abundantly to you-ward."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.13","order":"03.10.001.18420"},["b","13"],"For we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"write"],"none other things unto you, than what ye read or acknowledge; and I trust ye shall acknowledge even to the end;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.14","order":"03.10.001.18421"},["b","14"],"As also ye have acknowledged us in part, that we are your rejoicing, even as ye also",["i","are"],"ours in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"day"],"of the Lord Jesus."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.15","order":"03.10.001.18422"},["b","15"],"And in this confidence I was minded to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"come"],"unto you before, that ye might have a second benefit;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.16","order":"03.10.001.18423"},["b","16"],"And to pass by you into Macedonia, and to come again out of Macedonia unto you, and of you to be brought on my way toward Judæa."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.17","order":"03.10.001.18424"},["b","17"],"When I therefore was thus minded, did I use",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"lightness"],"? or the things that I purpose, do I purpose according to the flesh, that with me there should be yea yea, and nay nay?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.18","order":"03.10.001.18425"},["b","18"],"But",["i","as"],"God",["i","is"],"true, our word toward you was not yea and nay."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.19","order":"03.10.001.18426"},["b","19"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Son of God"],", Jesus Christ, who was preached among you by us,",["i","even"],"by me and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Silvanus"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"Timotheus"],", was not yea and nay, but in him was yea."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.20","order":"03.10.001.18427"},["b","20"],"For all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"promises"],"of God in him",["i","are"],"yea, and in him Amen, unto the glory of God by us."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.21","order":"03.10.001.18428"},["b","21"],"Now he which stablisheth us with you in Christ, and hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"anointed"],"us,",["i","is"],"God;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.22","order":"03.10.001.18429"},["b","22"],"Who hath also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"sealed"],"us, and given the earnest of the Spirit in our hearts."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.23","order":"03.10.001.18430"},["b","23"],"Moreover I call God for a record upon my soul, that to spare you I came not as yet unto Corinth."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.24","order":"03.10.001.18431"},["b","24"],"Not for that we have dominion over your faith, but are helpers of your joy: for by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"faith"],"ye stand."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.1a","order":"03.10.001.18432"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/21.1"},"D&C 21:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.3a","order":"03.10.001.18434"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-mercy-of"},"TG God, Mercy of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.3b","order":"03.10.001.18436"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/comfort"},"TG Comfort"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.4a","order":"03.10.001.18438"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/tribulation"},"TG Tribulation"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.4b","order":"03.10.001.18440"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/3.10"},"Philip. 3:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/2.16"},"2 Thes. 2:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.5a","order":"03.10.001.18442"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.24"},"Col. 1:24"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.6a","order":"03.10.001.18444"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"active, operative."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.6b","order":"03.10.001.18446"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.20"},"D&C 63:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.35"},"101:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.7a","order":"03.10.001.18448"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.8a","order":"03.10.001.18450"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/despair"},"TG Despair"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.9a","order":"03.10.001.18452"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.10a","order":"03.10.001.18454"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.11a","order":"03.10.001.18456"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.19"},"Philip. 1:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.22"},"Philem. 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.12a","order":"03.10.001.18458"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"TG Testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.12b","order":"03.10.001.18460"},["b","12b"],["span.small","GR"],"plainness, singleness of heart."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.12c","order":"03.10.001.18462"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.13"},"1 Cor. 2:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.13a","order":"03.10.001.18464"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.14a","order":"03.10.001.18466"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.9.8-10"},"D&C 1:9 (8–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.15a","order":"03.10.001.18468"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.7.5-7"},"1 Cor. 16:7 (5–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.17a","order":"03.10.001.18470"},["b","17a"],["span.small","GR"],"light-mindedness, levity."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.19a","order":"03.10.001.18472"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.35"},"Luke 1:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.19b","order":"03.10.001.18474"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.34.32-34"},"Acts 15:34 (32–34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.1"},"1 Thes. 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/5.12"},"1 Pet. 5:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.19c","order":"03.10.001.18476"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.10.10-11"},"1 Cor. 16:10 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.2"},"1 Thes. 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.20a","order":"03.10.001.18478"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.8"},"Rom. 15:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.21a","order":"03.10.001.18480"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/anointing"},"TG Anointing"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.22a","order":"03.10.001.18482"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sealing"},"TG Sealing"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.24a","order":"03.10.001.18484"},["b